---
title: Gochujang Pulled Chicken and Mushroom Pie with Sesame Chips and Salad
description: A comfort food classic using premium ingredients, this Gochujang Pulled Chicken and Mushroom Pie brings the best of the British pub into your kitchen.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R33_W21_UK_SG18603-3_Main_low-b928abc0.jpg
